	o eleven can search for eggs that can be exchanged for candy at multiple l
	ocations throughout the event. Enjoy photos with the Easter Bunny\, family
	 friendly activities and games! Join us for the FREE community event at th
	e Heatherwood Middle School track \\(1419 Trillium Blvd. SE\, Mill Creek\\
